description.en:
oinoNIA is a tokenized venture capital fund investing in promising FinTech / Blockchain projects, and other cryptocurrencies / ICOs. For projects with tokenization features, we will provide additional financial acceleration by launching separate ICOs.

NIA token holders will receive 20% of digital assets (tokens) from the pool of each subsequent ICO which will be launched by KoinoNIA fund. We help monetize interesting projects based on our strong investment and business experience.
